This one is based on a certain scene of a video about the time Tom, Jake, Z and Jacob were at...
body:
Ballet Spider-Man! ❤️🕷️🖤

This one is based on a certain scene of a video about the time Tom, Jake, Z and Jacob were at Disneyland in which Tom does the spinning with his Spidey suit. He looked adorable, so I had to draw him 😍😍❤️❤️

As a bonus, there’s this sketch of Spider-Gwen and MCU Spider-Man getting along thanks to their ballet skills 💃🕺💕
